{"tid":449434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民提26修訂阻封殺拉布","createTime":"2017-10-27T07:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T09:05:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9df5ea770b1991732648af226ba58bf540555f05","tid":449434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195959&d=eUE%2BeL1Xlivs6JdDGUmlLtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6cc8e29a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195959&h=6e043f34\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195959</a><br />\n<br />\n泛民提26修訂阻封殺拉布<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171027/large/27ls2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F27ls2p3.jpg&h=8c97c689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫乃光<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派力阻建制派收緊財會議事規則，民主派3名議員昨提共26項涉及修改財委會、該會轄下人事編制小組委員會及工務小組委員會會議程序建議。<br />\n<br />\n早前廖長江提出多項封殺民主派在財會拉布修訂，包括限制每名議員針對每項議程最多只能提出1項臨時動議，其他議員不得對該動議提修訂。而專業議政莫乃光、人民力量陳志全、民主黨尹兆堅昨向財會共提26項修訂，盼拖延處理廖的修訂。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波昨稱收到泛民相關修訂，要先看是否符合規程，希望一至兩個星期內有裁決。陳又指會按議員提交修訂時間先後處理有關修訂，所以會先處理廖的修訂。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫劍弦"},{"pid":"958d37daecd50ec974e9b992d213b23ffdc8bc51","tid":449434,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"話唔定又合併討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aa1685ab1dcd2a0fd03a2dc237dd9167a96352","tid":449434,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話唔定又合併討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳健波都講到明係想直接封殺泛民，所以可能連合併都廢事，直接唔比修定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}